  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Witch Hex</strong><br/><br/><p>The witch can touch a creature to suppress or protect it from negative conditions. The witch chooses one of the following conditions each time she uses this hex: dazzled, fatigued, shaken, or sickened. If the target is or later becomes afflicted with the chosen condition, that condition is suppressed for a number of minutes equal to the witch's level. Alternatively, the witch can grant her target a +4 circumstance bonus on saving throws against effects that cause any two of the listed conditions (which condition is always the witch's choice) for 24 hours. Once a creature has benefited from this hex, it cannot benefit from the hex again for 24 hours.</p>",
